<!DOCTYPE html>
%html
  %head
    %meta{content: "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}
  %body
    .indented.text-center
      %h2= "Hey #{@user.get_name_or_email}"

      .text-center
        %p It's been over a month since we launched.
      .text-left
        %span= "We have been busy and we are excited to say we have onboarded #{Adventure.approved.count}" 
        %a{href: "#{root_url}/adventures"} adventures
        in over 17 countries and we are super grateful you joined our network. We will send you updates that help our hosts - soon to come is a feature to simply customize each adventure that you offer. Please feel free to send us feedback about the platform, cool ideas, or just say hello. Simply reply to this email.

        %br
        %br
        .divider.divider-border

        %hw.text-center Here are a few tools you can use to share your Advlo pages. 
        %table#main{border: "0", cellpadding: "0", cellspacing: "20", width: "100%"}
          %tr
            %td
              - @user.adventures.approved.each do |adventure|
                %a{href: "#{root_url}adventures/#{adventure.slug}", style: 'text-decoration: none; color: #000; width: 35%; float: left;'}
                  %img{alt: adventure.title, height: "auto", src: adventure.attachment.url(:medium)}
                  

                  .share-links{style: 'width: 65%; float: right;'}
                    - share_url = "#{root_url}adventures/#{adventure.slug}"

                    %a{href:"http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?s=100&p[title]=" + adventure.title + '&p[summary]=' + adventure.summary[0..50] + '&p[url]=' + share_url}= image_tag "#{root_url}/assets/fb-email-bd69e985af97389bf052774e3531541b.png"

                    %a{href:"https://twitter.com/share?url=" + share_url + "&text=" + "Check out my adventure " + adventure.title + ' on Adventure Local'}= image_tag "#{root_url}/assets/twitter-email-f21c89929bcdb0751198c7318d9e7f53.png"

                    %a.btn.btn-default.social_btn.gp{href: "https://plus.google.com/share?url=#{share_url}"}= image_tag "#{root_url}/assets/gplus-email-5b11f1098ffab2a77fbae3f5f519811b.png"


                .text-left{style: 'word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 12px; width: 120px; margin-left: -25px;'}= adventure.title


        .divider.divider-border
        %br
        %br

      %i Safe travels,
      %br
      %a{href: "#{root_url}about"} The Advlo Team